ervice announcement. >last week they were in denver. maybe the ap person in denver did this >(remember, they just started with mlb out there). check tomorrow's >paper (4/21) and see if the person who is doing it from shea does the >same thing. >-- noel rappin noel@chaos.cs.brandeis.edu
